Taxing authorities may classify funds raised as taxable income to the Campaigner and any beneficiary who will receive funds directly from the applicable campaign. Hrtaa shall not be liable for any taxes payable on the contributions received. Hrtaa will ask for the personal account number / tax identification number (e.g., PAN) of Campaigners and any beneficiaries so that we may report taxable income to the relevant taxing authorities.

